{"tha-ap220:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap220:0.2":"Hatthivagga ","tha-ap220:0.3":"Akkantasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap220:1.1":"“Kusatakam gahetvana, ","tha-ap220:1.2":"upajjhayassaham pure; ","tha-ap220:1.3":"Mantanca anusikkhami, ","tha-ap220:1.4":"ganthadosassa pattiya. ","tha-ap220:2.1":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap220:2.2":"Ahutinam patiggaham; ","tha-ap220:2.3":"Usabham pavaram aggam, ","tha-ap220:2.4":"Tissam buddham ganuttamam. ","tha-ap220:3.1":"Kusatakam pattharitam, ","tha-ap220:3.2":"akkamantam naruttamam; ","tha-ap220:3.3":"Samuggatam mahaviram, ","tha-ap220:3.4":"lokajettham narasabham. ","tha-ap220:4.1":"Disva tam lokapajjotam, ","tha-ap220:4.2":"vimalam candasannibham; ","tha-ap220:4.3":"Avandim satthuno pade, ","tha-ap220:4.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap220:5.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap220:5.2":"yam adasim kusatakam; ","tha-ap220:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap220:5.4":"kusatakassidam phalam. ","tha-ap220:6.1":"Sattatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap220:6.2":"eko asim janadhipo; ","tha-ap220:6.3":"Sunando nama namena, ","tha-ap220:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap220:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap220:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap220:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap220:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma akkantasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap220:9.1":"Akkantasannakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}